      "text_excerpt": "Modern information systems1 can include a variety of computing platforms (e.g., industrial control systems, general purpose computing systems, cyber-physical systems, super computers, weapons systems, communications systems, environmental control systems, medical devices, embedded devices, sensors, and mobile devices such as smart phones and tablets). These platforms all share a common foundation\u2014computers with complex hardware, software and firmware providing a capability that supports the esse"
